craftable in jewellery, made for UNP body
contains chains version (4 colors, top and belt), spikes version (2 colors, navel, nipple and bottom), hearts version ( 3 colors, navel, nipple and bottom), spheres version (4 color  variants, navel, nipple and bottom) hearts with wings ( 2 colors, navel, nipple and bottom)

I don't give permission to upload it in steam.
